ass=\"label\">Industry</span><span class=\"value\">Tech</span></div></div></div></div></span><a class=\"get-started-button\" data-label=\"Article In Content: Offering Get Started\" href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/go/elf-labs-offering/\" rel=\"noopener sponsored nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Get Offer <div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M440.6 273.4c4.7-4.5 7.4-10.8 7.4-17.4s-2.7-12.8-7.4-17.4l-176-168c-9.6-9.2-24.8-8.8-33.9 .8s-8.8 24.8 .8 33.9L364.1 232 24 232c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24s10.7 24 24 24l340.1 0L231.4 406.6c-9.6 9.2-9.9 24.3-.8 33.9s24.3 9.9 33.9 .8l176-168z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></a></div></div></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"carousel-pagination\"><div class=\"splide__arrows\"><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev page-left-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M15 239c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9L207 465c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0s9.4-24.6 0-33.9L65.9 256 241 81c9.4-9.4 9.4-24.6 0-33.9s-24.6-9.4-33.9 0L15 239z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--next page-right-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M305 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L113 465c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0s-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l175-175L79 81c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9s24.6-9.4 33.9 0L305 239z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Biden has faced growing scrutiny over his health in the weeks since his diagnosis with Stage 4 prostate cancer while in office.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"nativo-placement-in-content-ap\"></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Earlier in May 2025, Biden criticized Trump’s rhetoric and <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/25/05/45278880/biden-says-trump-is-not-behaving-like-a-republican-president-slams-his-words-as-beneath-america-adds-thats-not-who-we-are-and-warns-of-his-modern-day-appeasement-of-putin\" target=\"_blank\">foreign policy</a> in an interview with BBC's <strong>Nick Robinson</strong>. He expressed disapproval of Trump’s remarks about possibly acquiring Greenland or making Canada the 51st state.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">These events highlight the ongoing tension between the two political figures, with Trump’s allegations serving as a distraction, according to Biden, from pressing issues facing the nation.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45786416\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>READ MORE:</strong> <a href=\"https://benzinga.com/markets/tech/25/06/45785192/anthony-scaramucci-says-the-left-should-focus-on-why-it-lost-elon-musk-rather-than-demonizing-him-cr\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Anthony Scaramucci Says The Left Should Focus On Why It Lost Elon Musk Rather Than ‘Demonizing’ Him: Credits Tesla CEO For ‘Enormously Positive’ Impact On Humanity</a></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><em>Image via Shutterstock</em></p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--></div></div>",
